采样能力，提高采样效率；提前发布核酸检测提示，分时分批组织群众采样；通过设置「两米线」、硬隔离、加强现场巡查等方式，加强现场采样点秩序维护；规范工作人员防护服穿脱，严格采样操作规范，防止因采样不规范而发生交叉感染。 截至目前，未发现因参加区域核酸筛查而感染的情况。北京：未发现因参加区域核酸筛查而感染的情况"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-60c8257fbc11e7e21109ee2eeb1e76ce_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/531878598"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIw7OQxPDor60BEAMaCDgwNDc3MjYzIICU3pMGMAE4kAFAMHIJNTMxODc4NTk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1652080170.5516562", "card_id": "Q_531896625", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "5 月 8 日四川绵阳市北川县发生 4.1 级地震，震源深度 8 千米，情况如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国地震台网正式测定：05 月 08 日 19 时 59 分在四川绵阳市北川县（北纬 31.89 度，东经 104.46 度）发生 4.1 级地震，震源深度 8 千米。（总台记者 贾宜超）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d8b91bb9b7a61e9e657c2e5bb3d52c7c_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/531896625"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIw7OQxPDor60BEAMaCDgwNDgxMjQ0IPbo3pMGMAA4N0Axcgk1MzE4OTY2MjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 20}